ZGC2LX.name: ZGC › LX
ZGC2LX.subwayRoutes:
Subway Hours to LX 5:57 - 22:20* (RMB 7)

Line 4: Weigongcun > National Library
　Interchange to Line 9 on the same platform
Line 9: National Library > Guogongzhuang
　Interchange to Fangshan Line on the same platform
Fangshan Line: Guogongzhuang > Liangxiang University Town North
　Exit A, walk to the campus or wait for the shuttle bus
* The last train time is estimated, and because several interchanges are required, the actual deadline may be later

LX2ZGC.name: LX › ZGC
LX2ZGC.subwayRoutes:
Subway Hours to ZGC 5:24 - 22:09 (RMB 7)

Walk to the station or wait for the shuttle bus
Fangshan Line: Liangxiang University Town North > Guogongzhuang
　Interchange to Line 9 on the same platform
Line 9: Guogongzhuang > National Library
　Interchange to Line 4 on the same platform (To Anheqiao North)
Line 4: National Library > Weigongcun
Exit A, and go upstairs and straight ahead to the campus east gate
